com.jess.arms.widget.boxing

类 Boxing

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jess.arms.widget.boxing.Boxing

  • public class Boxing
extends Object
    An entry for AbsBoxingActivity and AbsBoxingViewFragment.
    1.call of(BoxingConfig) to pick a mode.
    2.to use AbsBoxingActivity + AbsBoxingViewFragment combination, call withIntent(Context, Class) to make a intent and start(Activity) to start a new Activity.
    to use AbsBoxingViewFragment only, just call setupFragment(AbsBoxingViewFragment, OnBoxingFinishListener).
    3 4.to get result from a new Activity, call getResult(Intent) in Activity.onActivityResult(int, int, Intent).
    作者:
    ChenSL
